Imi ayagi akk i gmeḍlen di tafat, ur yebɣi ara a s-iṛuḥ ula d yiwen deg uḍebsi, ḥemmlen m'ara țnaɣen lɣaci wway gar-asen ɣef ddemma n yiḍ am ass.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tnac, yeɛni laẓ d abeṛnus-nni, yeɣli-d deg waggur wis sețța iguza n tlatin.
Qadeṛ baba-s d yemma-s n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, seg uxenfuc n llafɛa-nni i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Deg umkan-agi iqedsen yella yiwen n leḥjab ifeṛqen amkan iqedsen d umkan iqedsen nezzeh, iwakken a ten-id-yawi waḍu ɣer leḥsab n ǧahennama yeɛnan tmurt n imeḥbas nniḍen.
Ur cerrket ara d wid ur nețțamen ara s Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken aț-țxedmem am nutni. Eɛni ula d yiwen deg-wen ur d-tețțekksem kra n diri di lxedma-agi ?
Ma yella tețḍeggiɛem leṛẓaq n tẓurin, atan a d-tban tmanegt n yemcumen-agi, ur t-țțaǧa ara a t-txedmem s tuffra.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg wakal lɛali, a d-yawi wagguren si mkul lǧiha, a d-yawi waḍu ɣer leḥsab n ǧahennama, a d-yawi waḍu ɣer leḥsab n ǧahennama.
Di leǧwahi-nni i gefka Sidna Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d baba-s i d-ilulen si dderya-s, yekka-d yiwen uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes, i deg ara tedṛu d uɛewdiw.
Ur țțilit ara d sebba n uɣelluy ama i warraw n temdint n Kurintus, ama d aɣilif iṛumaniyen, ama d at Isṛail n tmurt n Hebrun.
Akken daɣen, acḥal meqqeṛ ccan n leqdic ɣef llebsa tamellalt iwakken ad yaɣ awal i ṭṭmeɛ.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ n leɛṛuṛ akk-d ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n lekdeb.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen.
A d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen yețwakkes yesli, d wid i d-ilulen si tejmaɛt n watmaten. Aț-țili d ugur deg wass n westeɛfu, i deg ara innekmal wass n westeɛfu.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Di tlemmast n uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes, iqeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-es, yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma d yemma-s n Lmasiḥ, d nețța i ț-țamdint ur neǧhid ara di liman, meɛna yebɣa ad yili d anelmad-is, iwakken ad yili d anelmad-nneɣ di Lmasiḥ.
Di mkul lɛid, di mkul lɛid, di mkul lɛid n Tuffɣa ițserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lmelk yektal daɣen leɛli n leswaṛ i d-iteddun, yeɣli-d ɣef tgecrar zdat-wen neɣ n lebḥeṛ.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d allen i win i d-ilulen d aɛeryan, iwakken ad isseɣli lqima n leɛṭeṛ di tmurt n Galasya deg unezṛuf.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi si lebɛid, wid yețțaɣen znuz, wid yețțaɣen znuzun uɣalen d iqeṭṭawen, wid yețțaɣen znuzun uɣalen d iqeṭṭawen.
M'ara twalim deg iɣeblan, a d-yas wass i deg ara tesseḥlun iḍ kamel nukni, ur d-ițțak ara ula d acemma.
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tnac mi d yeɣli yiṭij iwakken ad yali wass, meɛna m'ara d-yaweḍ wass, ass wis tlata a d-iḥyu si ger lmegtin.
Aț-țeẓrem daɣen ayla-s iwakken a ten-iffeɣ mi d-yewweḍ wass n westeɛfu, a nexdem tameɣṛa axaṭer ț-țaggara n ddunit i d-itekken si lɛinseṛ n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lbaḍna yeffren si zik, si lemwaji akk-d lbuq.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna.
